<p>In Boelen and van den Hout’s article, The Role of Threatening Misinterpretations and Avoidance in Emotional Problems After Loss (2008), they write the following sentence (from Statistical analyses): ‘As recommended by Aiken and West, in all regression analyses, predictors were centred to reduce ….’. What should be filled in to complete the sentence correctly?</p>
</p>]]></text>
